*bsdiff-4.3-r2 (13 Dec 2010)

  13 Dec 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +bsdiff-4.3-r2.ebuild:
  Revision bump to make sure that hte package is built with large file support
  on 32-bit architectures (it wasn't before, even though it was intended to).
  Make build verbose to avoid further mistakes slipping by as it happened
  before. Add die clauses to install while at it, and bump to EAPI=2.

  19 Oct 2010; Mart Raudsepp <leio@gentoo.org> bsdiff-4.3-r1.ebuild:
