  Removing 4.2 per ferringb's request.  4.3 has the same keywords

*bsdiff-4.3 (17 Sep 2005)

  17 Sep 2005: Brian Harring <ferringb@gentoo.org>: +bsdiff-4.3.ebuild
  -bsdiff-4.1.ebuild.
  Version bump, something of a maintenance release it seems. 
  Changes between 4.2 and 4.3 come down to using libbz2 rather then piping to
  bzip2.

